name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: ftp.client-write-packet-size
description: Packet size for clients to write

name: dfs.client.mmap.retry.timeout.ms
description:
The minimum amount of time that we will wait before retrying a failed mmap
    operation.

name: dfs.namenode.blockreport.max.lock.hold.time
description: The BlockReportProcessingThread max write lock hold time in ms.

name: dfs.webhdfs.netty.high.watermark
description: High watermark configuration to Netty for Datanode WebHdfs.

name: dfs.short.circuit.shared.memory.watcher.interrupt.check.ms
description:
The length of time in milliseconds that the short-circuit shared memory
    watcher will go between checking for java interruptions sent from other
    threads.  This is provided mainly for unit tests.

name: dfs.client.test.drop.namenode.response.number
description:
The number of Namenode responses dropped by DFSClient for each RPC call.  Used
    for testing the NN retry cache.

name: dfs.namenode.blockreport.queue.size
description: The queue size of BlockReportProcessingThread in BlockManager.
